      "Target_Variable": "Universal_Statement",
      "Med_Class_ID": "",
      "Route_Icon": "",
      "Statement_Text": "This is an infection of the upper breathing tubes, involving the nose, sinuses, throat, and voice box. It is mostly caused by a virus.",
